msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Sega Master System controller"
msgstr "Ovladač Sega Master System"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The Master System, originally named the Mark III, was released by Sega in 1985. As of 2015, the Master System is the longest-lived game console due to its surging popularity in Brazil."
msgstr "Master System, původně nazvaný Mark III, vydala společnost Sega v roce 1985. Od roku 2015 je Master System díky prudce rostoucí popularitě v Brazílii herní konzolí s nejdelší životností."

